# =============================================================================
# 2026-06-15 PRODUCTIZATION SCRUB -- data/ + vault/ are LOCAL-ONLY.
#   Betting ledgers / bankroll / CLV / live-bets / scraped odds were tracked on
#   the public origin before this; they are now untracked (kept on disk) and
#   these wholesale ignores stop any future `git add data/` from re-publishing
#   them. Only a short, audited, NON-betting whitelist stays tracked:
#   data/models/*metrics*.json + meta + hyperparams (model-quality evidence),
#   data/nba/{team_stats,player_avgs}_*.json (seed stats), data/{jersey_name_map,
#   team_colors}.json (reference maps), data/README.md, data/__init__.py.
#   Real per-sport corpora live local under data/domains/ (gitignored); tiny
#   committed proof fixtures live under tests/fixtures/ (NOT data/).
# =============================================================================
# Ignore the entire data/ tree, then re-include ONLY the audited non-betting whitelist.
# (Last-match-wins; this block is authoritative over the sprawling rules above.)
data/*
!data/README.md
!data/__init__.py
!data/jersey_name_map.json
!data/team_colors.json
!data/models/
data/models/*
!data/models/.gitkeep
!data/models/model_registry.json
!data/models/*_metrics.json
!data/models/hyperparams_*.json
!data/models/prop_corr_matrix.json
!data/models/props_stl_v2_metrics.json
!data/models/matchup_model_meta.json
!data/models/dnp_model_meta.json
!data/models/probe_defender_feature.json
!data/models/load_management.json
!data/nba/
data/nba/*
!data/nba/team_stats_*.json
!data/nba/player_avgs_*.json

